            "content_html": "\n  <p>\n    Avec la police wingdings, chaque lettre/chiffre/accent/etc est transformé en un symbole.<br><br>Regarde ça :\n  </p>\n\n    <figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\">\n      <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110152.png\" height=\"522\" width=\"601\" alt=\"\"  sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110152-xs.png 640w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110152-sm.png 768w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110152-md.png 1024w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110152-lg.png 1366w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110152-xl.png 1600w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110152-2xl.png 1920w\">\n      \n    </figure>\n\n  <p>\n    Donc si tu veux crypter \"Salut!\", ça donnera ça :\n  </p>\n\n    <figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\">\n      <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110254.png\" height=\"146\" width=\"519\" alt=\"\"  sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" srcset=\"https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110254-xs.png 640w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110254-sm.png 768w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110254-md.png 1024w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110254-lg.png 1366w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110254-xl.png 1600w ,https://graines2tech.github.io/eg-virtuel/media/posts/8/responsive/Capture-decran-2025-11-26-110254-2xl.png 1920w\">\n      \n    </figure>\n\n  <p>\n    Cool, non?\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Si tu l'utilises pour un mot de passe, <mark><strong>fais attention aux majuscules et minuscules</strong></mark>!\n  </p>",
